{"tid":1288664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同樂觀派嘅大家講！為時未晚！","createTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T18:30:09.000Z","uid":183751,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f01a31a8f4cb2cd05d3da3ba892715b1cddb218","tid":1288664,"uid":183751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"今日去左打泰拳 係久違嘅身心舒暢<br />\n自從果一日 腦同個身體都好似shut down左咁<br />\n放緊sem break 日日都訓係床度 連煲劇都覺得好攰<br />\n<br />\n老實啲講自己果晚太多野唔敢做<br />\n淨係敢傳下物資 守係出面<br />\n成日同自己講已經盡左力<br />\n其實無非都係想自己好過啲姐<br />\n<br />\n升旗禮果朝我訓過龍<br />\n一醒左果刻真係急到喊左出黎<br />\n真係好對唔住大家 好對唔住大家<br />\n訓係床度真係好糾結 好想連遊行都唔去<br />\n好想俾自己再難過啲 內疚啲 差愧一啲<br />\n如果唔係點對得住為香港犧牲左嘅三個人同好多人<br />\n好想憤斥自己 唔好再以為大家同自己已經做得好好了<br />\n<br />\n樂觀派一旦無左活力同希望 <br />\n就等於無左全世界<br />\n<br />\n如果你同我一樣 都係一貫嘅樂觀派<br />\n習慣睇到事情好嘅一面 <br />\n請你無論如何 絕對唔好絕望同頹落去<br />\n因為你已經係最有能力打起精神嘅果班人啦<br />\n做我地嘅啦啦隊 用我地嘅正能量影響大家<br />\n<br />\n知道大家每次念翻個心都會好痛好痛<br />\n路還很長 曙光一直都在身邊<br />\n七月一日絕非終局之戰 <br />\n<br />\n為時未晚 命數未有定稿<br />\n一切還看造化 <br />\n<br />\n同朋友一齊整左段片抒發下呢幾日以黎嘅情緒<br />\n繼續努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hZZLOYB7YjA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhZZLOYB7YjA&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=e9eda05e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hZZLOYB7YjA</a>"},{"pid":"60f7ee342683c1cd664bbbaee1a1e84a26d3d8cb","tid":1288664,"uid":183751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T17:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc64b59b9397360e88cd01c82da7694e1c6c66b","tid":1288664,"uid":5690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6sBCb6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6sBCb6.png&h=6415dba2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f658b1bc01fd87ee62b5aff1e4c86062f0758c3b","tid":1288664,"uid":183751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3426fbc754c5b96d1e36de3a67e32a71552b1d3","tid":1288664,"uid":183751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d304f71799bac20fb4d3c0cc0159271d48ebed4f","tid":1288664,"uid":183751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T18:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}